org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.ucm.profile.UCMProfile.ucm_technicalpolicies

Interface Ucm_technicalpoliciesPackage.Literals

  • Enclosing interface:
    Ucm_technicalpoliciesPackage

    public static interface Ucm_technicalpoliciesPackage.Literals
    Defines literals for the meta objects that represent
    • each class,
    • each feature of each class,
    • each operation of each class,
    • each enum,
    • and each data type
